                <category id="category_1">
                    <catName>Graffiti</catName>
                    <item id="item_1">It’s a type of street art.</item>
                    <item id="item_2">It’s found on walls in cities.</item>
                    <item id="item_3">The artists usually use colorful paints.</item>
                    <item id="item_4">Artists write words and paint pictures.</item>
                    <item id="item_5">Artists usually work very quickly.</item>
                    <item id="item_6">It lasts a long time and is difficult to remove.</item>
                </category>
                <category id="category_2">
                    <catName>Sand art</catName>
                    <item id="item_7">It’s usually done on beaches.</item>
                    <item id="item_8">The artists make models.</item>
                    <item id="item_9">Sand and water are used.</item>
                    <item id="item_10">Popular shapes are animals, people, and castles.</item>
                    <item id="item_11">Artists have to be very patient.</item>
                    <item id="item_12">It disappears when it rains.</item>
                </category>
